description:
Crypto Jade (JADE) at conception was an ERC-20 token on the Ethereum blockchain.

Jade Coin will run on a Proof-of-Work (PoW) system allowing it to be mineable.

Following the deployment of the blockchain, project will put together a mining
guide/package available for our community members to download to allow easy
access to cryptocurrency mining on our network for everyone, regardless of technical ability.
name: Jade Currency
